                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18700131-name-253" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18700131-name-253" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18700131-name-253" type="surname" value="SLADE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18700131-name-253" type="given" value="JOHN HENRY KINGSMAN"></interp>JOHN HENRY KINGSMAN SLADE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an iron-worker, of 19, Egro Street, St. John's—on the morning of 2nd December I was called by the police, and found my parlour shutters and window open—they had been closed and bolted when I went to bed—I missed a coat and blanket from the parlour—on 26th December I saw Samuel Allen wearing the coat, and gave him in charge—this is it; I have no doubt of it (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>).</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18700131-name-254" type="witnessName">
